\c 21
\s UJesu uzibonakalisa kubafundi bakhe elwandle lweTiberiyasi
\p
\v 1 Emva kwalezizinto uJesu wabuya wazibonakalisa\x + 7.4. 21.14. Mark. 16.12,14. Joha. 1.31.\x* kubafundi elwandle lweTiberiyasi\x + 6.1.\x*; njalo wazibonakalisa ngalindlela.
\v 2 Babendawonye oSimoni Petro, loTomasi othiwa nguDidimusi\x + 11.16.\x*, loNathaniyeli\x + 1.45.\x* oweKana yeGalili\x + 2.1.\x*, la\add madodana\add* kaZebediya, labanye ababili babafundi bakhe\x + Mat. 4.21. Luka 5.10.\x*.
\v 3 USimoni Petro wathi kubo: Ngiyagola inhlanzi. Bathi kuye: Lathi sizahamba lawe. Basebephuma bahle bangena emkhunjini\x + 21.25.\x*, kodwa ngalobobusuku kababambanga lutho\x + Luka 5.5.\x*.
\v 4 Kwathi sekusemadabukakusa uJesu wema ekhunjini\x + 20.19.\x*; kodwa abafundi babengazi ukuthi nguJesu\x + 20.14.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakho uJesu wathi kubo: Bantwana, lilokudla yini\x + 1 Joha. 2.13,18.\x*? Bamphendula \add bathi\add*: Hatshi\x + Luka 24.41.\x*.
\v 6 Wasesithi kubo: Phosani imbule ehlangothini lokunene lomkhumbi, njalo lizathola\x + Luka 5.4,6,7.\x*. Basebephosa, njalo babengaselakho ukulidonsa ngenxa yobunengi benhlanzi.
\v 7 Ngakho lowomfundi uJesu ayemthanda wathi kuPetro\x + 21.20. 13.23.\x*: YiNkosi. USimoni Petro, esezwile ukuthi yiNkosi, wagqoka isembatho\x + 13.4.\x* (ngoba wayenqunu\x + 1 Sam. 19.24.\x*), waseziphosela olwandle.
\v 8 Kodwa abanye abafundi beza ngomkolo\x + 6.22,23.\x*, bedonsa imbule lenhlanzi, ngoba babengekhatshana lomhlabathi, kodwa kungaba zingalo ezingamakhulu amabili.
\v 9 Kwathi sebekhuphukele emhlabathini, babona umlilo wamalahle\x + 18.18.\x* khona, lenhlanzi zibekwe phezu kwawo, lesinkwa\x + 6.9.\x*.
\v 10 UJesu wathi kubo: Lethani ezi\add nye\add* zezinhlanzi elisanda kuzibamba\x + 6.9.\x*.
\v 11 USimoni Petro wasekhwela, wahudulela imbule emhlabathini, ligcwele inhlanzi ezinkulu, ikhulu lamatshumi amahlanu lantathu; njalo lanxa zazinengi kangaka, imbule kalidabukanga\x + 21.3.\x*.
\v 12 UJesu wathi kubo: Wozani\x + Seb. 10.41.\x* lidle\x + 21.15. Mat. 22.4.\x*. Kodwa kakho kubafundi owaba lesibindi sokumbuza \add ukuthi\add*: Ungubani wena? besazi ukuthi yiNkosi.
\v 13 UJesu wasesiza\x + Seb. 10.41.\x*, wathatha isinkwa, wabanika, lenhlanzi ngokufananayo\x + Luka 24.30,43. Seb. 1. 4.\x*.
\v 14 Lokhu sekungokwesithathu uJesu ebonakaliswa\x + 20.19,26.\x* kubafundi, esevukile kwabafileyo\x + 20.19,26.\x*.
\s Ukholo lukaPetro
\p
\v 15 Sebedlile\x + 21.15. Mat. 22.4.\x*, uJesu wathi kuSimoni Petro: Simoni kaJona\x + Mat. 16.17. Luka 22.31,32.\x*, uyangithanda kulalaba yini\x + Mat. 26.33. Mark. 14.29.\x*? Wathi kuye: Yebo Nkosi; wena uyazi ukuthi ngiyakuthanda. Wathi kuye: Phana amawundlu ami ukudla.
\v 16 Wabuya wathi kuye ngokwesibili: Simoni kaJona, uyangithanda yini\x + Mat. 16.17. Luka 22.31,32.\x*? Wathi kuye: Yebo Nkosi, wena uyazi ukuthi ngiyakuthanda. Wathi kuye: Yelusa izimvu zami\x + Luka 12.32. Seb. 20.28. 1 Pet. 5.2. Joha. 10.11.\x*.
\v 17 Wathi kuye ngokwesithathu: Simoni kaJona, uyangithanda yini\x + Mat. 16.17. Luka 22.31,32.\x*? UPetro wadabuka ngoba wathi kuye ngokwesithathu: Uyangithanda yini\x + 13.38.\x*? Wasesithi kuye: Nkosi, wena uyakwazi konke; wena uyakwazi ukuthi ngiyakuthanda\x + 2.25.\x*. UJesu wathi kuye: Phana izimvu zami ukudla.
\v 18 Ngiqinisile, ngiqinisile, ngithi kuwe\x + 13.36.\x*: Usemutsha, wawuzibhinca, uhamba lapho othanda khona; kodwa nxa usumdala, uzakwelula izandla zakho, omunye abesekubopha, akuse lapho ongathandi khona\x + 21.7.\x*.
\v 19 Lalokhu wakutsho, etshengisa indlela yokufa\x + 2 Pet. 1.14.\x* ayezadumisa uNkulunkulu ngayo\x + 7.39. 12.33.\x*. Esetshilo lokhu wathi kuye: Ngilandela\x + 13.36. Mat. 4.19. 16.24.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UPetro etshibilika wabona umfundi uJesu amthandayo elandela\x + 13.23.\x*, yena futhi owayeyeme esifubeni sakhe ekudleni kwantambama wathi: Nkosi, ngubani ozakunikela\x + 13.25.\x*?
\v 21 Kwathi uPetro embona wathi kuJesu: Nkosi, lo-ke?
\v 22 UJesu wathi kuye: Uba ngithanda ukuthi ahlale\x + 1 Kor. 15.6. Fil. 1.25.\x* ngize ngifike, ulani lakho\x + Mat. 16.28. 1 Kor. 4.5. 11.26. Isam. 2.5. 3.11. 22.7,12,20.\x*? Ngilandela wena\x + 13.36. Mat. 4.19. 16.24.\x*.
\v 23 Ngakho lelilizwi laphumela kubazalwane, ukuthi lowomfundi kayikufa; kanti uJesu katshongo kuye ukuthi kayikufa; kodwa \add wathi\add*: Uba ngithanda ukuthi ahlale ngize ngifike, ulani lakho\x + Seb. 9.30. 10.23. 11.1,12,29. 12.17. 14.2. 15.1,3,22,23. 16.40. 17.6,10,14. 21.7. 28.14. Mat. 23.8.\x*?
\s Isicino
\p
\v 24 Nguye lowomfundi ofakaza ngalezizinto, lozibhalileyo; njalo siyazi\x + 1 Joha. 3.2,14. 5.15,18,19,20. Joha. 19.35.\x* ukuthi ubufakazi bakhe buliqiniso\x + 3 Joha. 12.\x*.
\v 25 Njalo zikhona lezinye izinto ezinengi uJesu azenzayo, uba bezilotshiwe zonke ngazinye\x + 20.30.\x*, ngicabanga ukuthi lomhlaba lawo\x + Amos 7.10.\x* ubungebe lendawo yezingwalo ezilotshiweyo. Ameni\x + 2.6. Mark. 2.2.\x*.
